## Deployment (Streamlit Community Cloud)

This app is deployed for free on **Streamlit Community Cloud**:

1. Push this repository (including `app.py`, `requirements.txt`, and `best.pt`) to a **public GitHub repo**.
   - If `best.pt` is larger than 100 MB, track it with [Git LFS](https://git-lfs.com/).
2. Go to [share.streamlit.io](https://share.streamlit.io) and sign in with GitHub.
3. Select your repository, branch, and `app.py` as the entry point.
4. Click **Deploy**. The first build takes a few minutes because `ultralytics` pulls in PyTorch.

Every push to the repo redeploys the app automatically.

